WEBVTT

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:30.100
“We are not responsible 
for this violence.”

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:32.740
“We do not accept the blame.”

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:36.640
And when we are free of blame, 
we will be freed from fear as well.

00:04:36.660 --> 00:04:41.700
(Applause)

00:04:43.480 --> 00:04:47.440
Nowadays, Action Heroes are
sleeping in their very own public parks.

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:53.160
Through the "Meet to Sleep" program,
Action Heroes across India

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:56.840
are challenging fear 
and saying that trust is bigger than fear.

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:59.480
To live free from fear is our right.